high_descs: turn around and face the stove
pick up the pot that is on the left back burner from the stove
turn around heads towards the refrigerator and face the fridge doors
open both fridge doors and put the pot inside on the right side on the top shelf, close the doors for a few seconds, open the doors, remove the pot and close the doors
turn back around and go across the room back to the stove
put the pot on the left back burner of the stove
anns.task_desc: put a chilled pot on the left back burner of the stove

high_descs: turn around and walk over to the kitchen stove
grab the pan off of the top left burner
turn around and walk to the refrigerator
place the pan inside of the fridge, let it cool for a bit, then take it back out
turn left and walk back over to the kitchen stove
put the cooled pan down on the back left burner
anns.task_desc: place a cooled pan on the back left burner

high_descs: Move a few feet to the right to the stove.
Pick up the silver pot from the back left burner.
Turn around and walk across the room to the fridge.
Put the pot on the top right shelf in the fridge. Close the door for a few seconds and take the pot back out.
Turn left and move back to the stove.
Place the pot on the back left burner on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled metal pot on the stove.
